b4a5ee3fba0b8aac555251d6","tid":2168794,"uid":218659,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"佢個樣都似監躉樣"},{"pid":"e2babf7dacb3e5f184148e584284ca186da0a354","tid":2168794,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"獌狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ca648836de761819e560f73ef0ba2bda9121d2","tid":2168794,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"依啲人有咩人性可言"},{"pid":"797572934ff361f9011a1004a0e22ed01568f491","tid":2168794,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a0a3f65fcd981cb10f8d740013ae5c92f157f2","tid":2168794,"uid":158145,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"曼聯傳統：錢可以解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"解決到就唔洗出局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e524f33efc2a1a648667d302cdf6d56ecb50302","tid":2168794,"uid":153400,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"太陽報》追蹤報導麥佳亞（Harry Maguire）被捕事件，稱事件起因是麥佳亞一行人與<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">曼城球迷</span></span>發生爭鬥，最終事件鬧大了。<br />\n<br />\n  當地時間週四晚，麥佳亞一行在酒吧與曼城球迷發生爭吵扭打。目擊者稱：「前一天晚上就有一群人對著麥佳亞叨叨，但那隻是玩笑。週四晚上，這些人變得更有侵略性了，他們衝著麥佳亞喊&lsquo;F*** United&rsquo;，他們試圖激怒他，還試圖騷擾同行的一些女孩。麥佳亞當時已經生氣了，那些人還在喊&lsquo;F*** United&rsquo;，然後開始和麥佳亞的同伴爭吵打鬥。那些人倒在地上後，麥佳亞踢了他們的背部，女孩們在尖叫。」<br />\n<br />\n  「兩個附近的警察過來試圖停止爭鬥，麥佳亞真的怒了。他衝警察喊&lsquo;去F***你們自己，這不關你們的事情。&rsquo;警察想要逮捕他，麥佳亞就開始打警察，警察不得不叫支援。又來了兩、三個警察，但是麥佳亞太強壯了，也太憤怒了，不能製服他。他一直衝著警察喊叫，警察真的挺難的，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">至少一名警察受傷了。最後用了超過五名警察才把他制服</span></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n  當地警方發言人稱：「3名外國遊客在米克諾斯島被捕，年齡分別是27歲，28歲，29歲。案件檔案已經公開，三名外國人涉嫌抗議執法、身體傷害以及言語侮辱警察、試圖賄賂警察等罪行。」<br />\n<br />\n  按照麥佳亞的律師的說法，他否認警察的指控，球員被移交地方檢察院審理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da732f3d0931327f69d9aad7e1a506f03a9192df","tid":2168794,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78a20bdda596b007b7e097dc5267c408c0d4d9ee","tid":2168794,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"拉啦 對準返政權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89e441971edaf2a9b57b1316889b98ec4f28948","tid":2168794,"uid":89037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"狗性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3323a99754b44a2fe97842aa288a879672f48971","tid":2168794,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1da18a9efd8c7eba54ecd9b2e1db6ad3537c4f7a","tid":2168794,"uid":248695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"8000萬鎊又冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"2020年仲有人信佢真係8000萬"},{"pid":"aed7d6ce7120bdf2494bc24f37fc46ca2cd70a8c","tid":2168794,"uid":51485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3323a99754b44a2fe97842aa288a879672f48971","tid":2168794,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1da18a9efd8c7eba54ecd9b2e1db6ad3537c4f7a","tid":2168794,"uid":248695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"8000萬鎊又冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":